reviews.text:
Every time I got holiday and travelled to Hong Kong,  I always came back at this underground restaurant. Crew Chinese staff they did not speak fluent to English but they are friendly and accommodating to all foreign customers. Serving food was great! Highly recommended to travelers to get cheaper price but all worth it. 
#RiceNoodles

Cuttlefish ball rice noodle (河粉) - The soup is lack of flavor, the cuttlefish ball was good, fresh made, texture is good. 

4 treasures rice noodle - same, my wife complained about lack of flavor as well. The 4 treasures were ok.
Typical Chinese cha chaan teng with nicer decor than most. Extensive menu. Efficient waiter, but not too friendly. Value for money.
service good and many choice of foods
Teochew fishball breakfast set is good.
